lead_paragraph: A breathtaking individual goal from Saul Niguez put Atletico Madrid in the box seat in their Champions League semi-final against Bayern Munich with a 1-0 victory in a tense first leg on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Saul Stunner Gives Atletico Advantage Over Bayern
